Aim:
To write a C program that sorts an array of numbers in ascending order using the Merge Sort

Algorithm:

Step 1:
Read the number of elements and store them in an array.

Step 2:
Call mergeSort(arr, 0, n-1).

Step 3 (Merge Sort):

If left < right:
1. Find the middle index.
2. Recursively sort the left half.
3. Recursively sort the right half.
4. Merge both sorted halves using merge().

Step 4 (Merge Function):

1. Compare elements from both halves.
2. Copy the smaller element into the temporary array.
3. Copy remaining elements from left or right.
4. Copy the merged elements back to the original array.

Step 5:
Print the sorted array.

Code:
#include <stdio.h>

// Merge two sorted subarrays
void merge(int arr[], int left, int mid, int right)
{
    int i = left;
    int j = mid + 1;
    int k = 0;

    int temp[right - left + 1];

    // Merge logic
    while (i <= mid && j <= right)
    {
        if (arr[i] < arr[j])
            temp[k++] = arr[i++];
        else
            temp[k++] = arr[j++];
    }

    // Copy left-out elements
    while (i <= mid)
        temp[k++] = arr[i++];

    while (j <= right)
        temp[k++] = arr[j++];

    // Copy temp back to original
    for (i = left, k = 0; i <= right; i++, k++)
        arr[i] = temp[k];
}

// Merge Sort function
void mergeSort(int arr[], int left, int right)
{
    if (left < right)
    {
        int mid = (left + right) / 2;
        mergeSort(arr, left, mid);      // Left part
        mergeSort(arr, mid + 1, right); // Right part
        merge(arr, left, mid, right);   // Merge halves
    }
}

int main()
{
    int n;
    printf("Enter number of elements: ");
    scanf("%d", &n);

    int arr[n];
    printf("Enter %d elements:\n", n);
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++)
        scanf("%d", &arr[i]);

    mergeSort(arr, 0, n - 1);

    printf("Sorted array (Merge Sort): ");
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++)
        printf("%d ", arr[i]);

    return 0;
}

Output:
Enter number of elements: 6
Enter 6 elements:
12 5 7 3 9 2
Sorted array (Merge Sort): 2 3 5 7 9 12

Result:
The program successfully sorts the given array in ascending order using the Merge Sort